Package: foodmap
Title: Map Australia's Best Restaurants from Multiple Guides
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Peter", "Owen", email = "peter@bzi.com.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Scrapes Australian and US restaurant guides (Broadsheet,
    Gourmet Traveller, Time Out, AGFG, Urban List, Good Food Guide,
    SMH GFG awards, Concrete Playground, The Infatuation, Eater, 7x7,
    Conde Nast Traveler, James Beard Awards, Michelin Guide), geocodes
    venues via the Google Places API, and exports KML, CSV, and
    interactive Leaflet HTML files.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3.9000
